{"tid":2384214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"需要現金周轉，問銀行借廿個","createTime":"2021-01-28T12:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T13:04:24.000Z","uid":140526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b45981612a14a2b2af5252b087a27bb0c2bb21af","tid":2384214,"uid":140526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"如題，武肺下，小生意失敗<br />\n上兩星期，上網申請x打銀行貸款，借18萬<br />\n同個sales傾咗幾次電話，交晒資料<br />\n終於有批核結果<br />\n<br />\n方案1.借22萬，分60期還，每月還5千（即8萬利息）<br />\n我自己就覺得太貴息，唔知大家點睇！？<br />\n<br />\n再問佢有冇平啲方案，當然就係咁耍我<br />\n咩60期，還得輕鬆啲，要借夠20萬以上先可以有咁平息，等等<br />\n<br />\n我明白，銀行都要賺息，但都即管問吓佢有冇更優惠方案<br />\n方案2.同樣金額，分48期還，每月還5千9（即6萬3息）<br />\n<br />\n我屌，差啲做咗傻仔<br />\n<br />\n可能聽我咁大反應，又話要同經理商量下<br />\n<br />\n最後我只係同佢講，我每月大概可以還幾多<br />\n叫佢提供一個最理想還款期數"},{"pid":"c80b7a7f92e75553ca3db27811d12f6c02c5fc1a","tid":2384214,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"搵大新"},{"pid":"886d47a0694410b941744149bd02f777c30b39e7","tid":2384214,"uid":81780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"你知唔知自己TU 係幾多？似TU 唔靚所以咁貴息"},{"pid":"95c70f965a97c991a555777ca2c745774ef6f5bc","tid":2384214,"uid":140526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c80b7a7f92e75553ca3db27811d12f6c02c5fc1a","tid":2384214,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"搵大新"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"都要貨比三家<br />\n睇吓邊間抵啲"},{"pid":"844bc470f866bfa1087a449930f43aec3bfda610","tid":2384214,"uid":140526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"886d47a0694410b941744149bd02f777c30b39e7","tid":2384214,"uid":81780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"你知唔知自己TU 係幾多？似TU 唔靚所以咁貴息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"唔知道<br />\n係咪要問啲信貸評級機構？"},{"pid":"445503c1bc33de045701eb1b3915f18ce36bcc71","tid":2384214,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"你信用卡呢，有冇limit<br />\n<br />\n信用金現金分期應該平d"},{"pid":"cebfe0cbbf6dc0fbdd025a500074df8b0c958558","tid":2384214,"uid":81780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.transunion.hk/zh/product/credit-report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transunion.hk%2Fzh%2Fproduct%2Fcredit-report&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=040c29bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.transunion.hk/zh/product/credit-report</a><br />\n<br />\n俾錢check，唔會影響評分，你就知點解咁高息<br />\n<br />\n但你去問多一間銀行評分就會跌，銀行批俾你的息會再貴啲"}]}